Wrong. I've said this before and i'll repeat it: before this patch, group exp was better  in pre-elemental planes zones. <br>
<br>
 i'm not talking about per mob experience, I'm talking about the time it takes to kill each mob is much less in Valor than say, Plane Of Earth, so at the end of a grouping session, you'll get 9+ AA's in POV in the time it takes you to get 7 in an Elemental Plane. The only advantage to grouping in the Elemental planes is it's less crowded and has better item drops. Soloing pre-patch is closer, because the time-of-kill factor is less prevalent. <br>
<br>
<br>
